OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and largely sunny morning.
OL,6,FCloud then builds from the southwest,
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells becoming more
OL,8,Flimited through the afternoon. Most
OL,9,Fparts staying dry, but the odd spot of
OL,10,Frain is possible in the west later.
OL,11,FTurning breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying cloudy and breezy
OL,14,Fduring the evening, with further
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain. Heavier and more
OL,16,Fpersistent rain spreads northeast
OL,17,Fafter midnight, clearing soon after
OL,18,Fdawn. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
