OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy start, perhaps some
OL,6,Fearly drizzle. Most parts dry and
OL,7,Frather warm, although the odd
OL,8,Fafternoon shower also possible. Heavy
OL,9,Frain and gusty winds move east into
OL,10,Fthe evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloudier
OL,14,FFriday, but mostly dry, before a
OL,15,Fweakening band of rain spreads east
OL,16,Flater. Sunny spells and showers
OL,17,FSaturday. Warm in any brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
